63}, {\"ngram\": \"partner\", \"from\": 6368, \"to\": 6375}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Three years ago, Marchand sent a cold-call email to Bowman asking if he could get a scholarship to swim for him at Arizona State.\", \"from\": 6394, \"to\": 6523, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6446, \"end\": 6452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\", \"score\": 0.9999766550005147, \"rank\": 2.3345544840091698e-05, \"text\": \"Bowman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\"}, {\"begin\": 6509, \"end\": 6522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona_State_University\", \"score\": 0.9316018201508562, \"rank\": 0.07341997156043975, \"text\": \"Arizona State\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona_State_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arizona_State_University\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Marchand\", \"from\": 6411, \"to\": 6419}, {\"ngram\": \"a cold-call email\", \"from\": 6425, \"to\": 6442}, {\"ngram\": \"a scholarship\", \"from\": 6476, \"to\": 6489}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bowman recognized the last name\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094Xavier Marchand, L\\u00c3\\u00a9on\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s father, was an Olympic swimmer in the 1990s\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094and the kid had solid times, so he took him onboard.\", \"from\": 6524, \"to\": 6683, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6524, \"end\": 6530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\", \"score\": 0.9999766550005147, \"rank\": 2.3345544840091698e-05, \"text\": \"Bowman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Bowman\"}, {\"begin\": 6558, \"end\": 6573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xavier_Marchand\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.